I get it...nice.

::Repugnus::
"Autobot, then why be we fighting fool.  I too, am an Autobot. "
He turns as the missiles roar by him.  He saw the attacker with his good 
vision.
"Let me help Autobot. YOUR MINE."  He runs at this new bot once again 
sending out distorted color waves to mess up the bots vision.

Yanshosh@... wrote:

> The blobs were the distorted versions of the pincers.
> 
> ::::
> 
> The bot growls as Repungus admits defeat.
> 
> "I'm no Decepticon. I'm an Autobot warrior," he says, instinctively 
> ducking as he hears the roar of missiles. One missile still slams into 
> one of his missile launchers, making him stumble back, the launcher 
> disabled. He fires two missiles from his remaining launcher past 
> Repungus, hoping to hit whatever was there.
> 
> 
>
